name: FyouNK x Grassroots Limited Edition Snapback - Purple
description:
Inspired by throwback styles of 1990's graphic snap backs, these hats are a homage to the sportswear caps you grew up loving and wearing. The inside lining of the grey and purple hats feature an original illustration titled "Syncopated Dream", which is a graphic interpretation of the "Syncopated Sleep" mix by Michigan-based ambient electronic producer A Unique Machine. For each of the hats, we wanted our patterns to stay true to that throwback style while still carrying the modern street wear aesthetic we strive for at FyouNK clothing - Freedom You Now Know. 

We are donating a portion of the proceeds to Children's Leukemia Foundation http://leukemiamichigan.org
